                            <li class="blog-text-overview margin-top-bottom normal">Longer battery life</li>
                            <li class="blog-text-overview margin-top-bottom normal">More powerful graphics</li>
                            <li class="blog-text-overview margin-top-bottom normal">Better display</li>
                        </ul>
